About the 'bcc-deps/' directory
--------------------------------

The files in 'bcc-deps/' are source files from the BCC repository that
BPFd makes use of.

They are not to be modified, and the only changes allowed to be made on these
files are when they are updated by their newer copies from the BCC repository.

These files as they are currently were pulled from the following fork of the
BCC repository at the following commit:

Repo: https://github.com/joelagnel/bcc/
Commit: cf07b81671039d82125ddf4a79a0c0a818073b1f
